# codebase-memory-mcp scope for champsim_v25
# Goal: index core simulator (src/ + inc/) only. Exclude dead code, build
# artifacts, results/logs, Windows build, and swappable algorithm variants
# that would overflood the graph.

# --- build artifacts / outputs / logs (no source) ---
bin/
.lto_cache/
_ckpt/
champsim_results/
ByP_LOOP_LOG/
profiles_v10/
win_deps/
docs/

# --- swappable algorithm module variants (out of src+inc scope) ---
branch/
prefetcher/
replacement/
tracer/

# --- Windows-specific build (not used in linux build) ---
Makefile.win
Makefile.win.clang
Makefile.win.clang.libstdcxx
qbuild_v14_win.sh
qrun_v14_win.sh

# --- empty / stub source (0 bytes, no functions) ---
src/instruction.cc

# --- analysis notes, not code ---
*.bounds.md
